snippet.title: RG Kar Verdict: Lawyer of Sanjay Roy, Kabita Sarkar, Makes Explosive Comments After Verdict
snippet.description:
RG Kar Verdict: বিচারপর্বে কী কথা সঞ্জয়ের সঙ্গে? কেন সঞ্জয় রায়ের পক্ষে কবিতা সরকার? বিস্ফোরক শিয়ালদহ আদালতের আইনজীবী। কী বললেন তিনি, ভিসেরা পরীক্ষার রিপোর্ট নিয়ে চাঞ্চল্যকর বয়ান শুনলে চমকে যাবেন!
Lawyer of Convicted Sanjay Roy, Kabita Sarkar, Makes Explosive Comments After Verdict. She said that from what she saw of Sanjay, she did not think he could commit such a heinous crime.

snippet.title: Darling -  Hilarious Back-to-Back Comedy Scenes | G.V. Prakash | Nikki Galrani | Karunas | Sun NXT
snippet.description:
Get ready for a rollercoaster of laughs and scares in this hilarious horror comedy scene from the movie "Darling." Watch as Karunas, G.V. snippet.title: R G Kar News : আমি যদি ধর্ষণ করতাম ...রায় ঘোষণার পর বিস্ফোরক Sanjay | Bangla News
snippet.description:
R G Kar News : আর জি করে দোষী সাব্যস্ত সঞ্জয় রাই। সোমবার সাজা ঘোষণা করবে আদালত। তরুণী চিকিৎসকের ধর্ষণ-খুনে রায়। সঞ্জয়কে দোষী সাব্যস্ত শিয়ালদা আদালতের। ৫ মাস পর আর জি করের রায়। ৯ অগাস্ট ২০২৪- আর জি করে ধর্ষণ-খুন। পরদিনই সঞ্জয়কে গ্রেফতার Kolkata Police র।

#rgkarnews #rgkarmedicalcollege #rgkarverdict #sanjayrai #cbi #sealdahcourt #banglanews #news18bangla 
n180c_kolkata

snippet.description:

पुलिस FIR के मुताबिक :

सैफ अली खान के घर में चोरी करने वाले व्यक्ति को लेकर जो बयान दर्ज किए गए हैं उसके मुताबिक 56 वर्षीय सैफ अली खान के घर की हाउस मेड ने बताया कि उसे बाथरूम के पास अचानक कोई परछाई नजर आई उसे लगा कि करीना शायद अपने छोटे बेटे को देखने आए होगी लेकिन उन्हें बाद में शक हुआ तो वह... आगे गई अचानक एक 35 से 40 वर्षीय अज्ञात व्यक्ति ने महिला के ऊपर हमला कर दिया और धारदार हथियार दिखाते हुए चुप रहने के लिए कहा इसी बीच दूसरी मेड भी आ गई... आरोपी से पूछा गया कि उसे क्या चाहिए उसने कहा कि एक करोड रुपए... इसी दौरान अगर बात की जाए तो सैफ अली खान जो बारहवें फ्लोर पर रहते हैं, वह भी नीचे आ गए उन्होंने जब देखा तो अज्ञात आरोपी और सैफ के बीच हाथापाई हुई जिसमें सैफ को शरीर के अलग-अलग हिस्सों पर छह जगहों पर चोट लगी.. जिसमें से एक नुकीला हथियार टूट कर सैफ के शरीर में भी अटक गया... इसी दौरान आरोपी को उन लोगों ने दूसरे कमरे में बंद भी कर दिया लेकिन जब सैफ को ज्यादा चोट लगी थी तब मेड और फैमिली के बाकी स्टाफ मेंबर्स ने इब्राहिम को बुलाया इब्राहिम और सारा अली खान भी आठवीं मंजिल पर ही रहते हैं वह ऊपर आए और सैफ अली खान को लेकर ऑटो में अस्पताल गए... अगर बात की जाए गाड़ी की तो उसे वक्त परिवार में कोई भी ड्राइवर मौजूद नहीं था और ऑटोमेटिक इलेक्ट्रिक वाहन फिलहाल किसी को चलाना नहीं आता था इसलिए आनन फानन में सैफ को लेकर वे लोग लीलावती अस्पताल पहुंचे।

snippet.title: EGG BONDA | MUTTAI BONDA | Road Side Evening Snacks Recipe Cooking In Village | Bajji Street Food
snippet.description:
In this video, we bring you the ultimate recipe for Egg Bonda (Muttai Bonda), a beloved roadside evening snack that everyone enjoys! Watch as we prepare this crispy, golden-brown delight in a traditional village setting, using fresh ingredients and time-honored cooking techniques.

The Egg Bonda is made by coating perfectly boiled eggs with a spiced gram flour batter and frying them to perfection. This mouthwatering snack is best enjoyed hot, with an evening. Whether you're a fan of street food or looking for a quick and tasty recipe to try at home, this video has you covered!

Get a glimpse of authentic village-style cooking and join us as we prepare this classic Indian snack in a scenic, peaceful atmosphere.

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1000305684

#samvishal #manimegalaihussain  #manimegalai  #mediamasons #shorts #samoduvilayadu #season4 

Samodu Vilayadu is back with a bang for Season 4! 🎉 In this grand premiere episode, the multi-talented Manimegalai  and her Husband, Choreographer Hussain  take on the ultimate movie-based challenge. From lightning-fast answers in ‘10 Endrathukulley’ to laugh-out-loud moments in ‘Nadiganda,’ this duo brings their A-game and unmatched energy!

Will they crack the dialogues in ‘Mudinjal Kandupudi,’ or will Sam’s tricks get the better of them? Watch now for unlimited fun, laughter, and surprises as Season 4 kicks off in style! Don’t miss the mother-daughter chemistry and their hilarious banter!

#samvishal #manimegalaihussain  #manimegalai  #mediamasons #shorts #samoduvilayadu #season4 

Samodu Vilayadu is back with a bang for Season 4! 🎉 In this grand premiere episode, the multi-talented Manimegalai  and her Husband, Choreographer Hussain  take on the ultimate movie-based challenge. From lightning-fast answers in ‘10 Endrathukulley’ to laugh-out-loud moments in ‘Nadiganda,’ this duo brings their A-game and unmatched energy!

Will they crack the dialogues in ‘Mudinjal Kandupudi,’ or will Sam’s tricks get the better of them? Watch now for unlimited fun, laughter, and surprises as Season 4 kicks off in style! Don’t miss the mother-daughter chemistry and their hilarious banter!

snippet.title: Every Web Series in Seconds | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Ever wished you could watch an entire web series in just a few seconds? Well, we made it happen! 🎬😂
In Every Web Series in Seconds, we take the most popular Indian and international web series and summarize their entire plots in the quickest, most hilarious way possible. Get ready for a rollercoaster of rapid recaps, savage one-liners, and absurdly accurate summaries that will leave you laughing out loud. Whether you’re a binge-watcher or someone who never made it past episode one, this video is for you!
Which web series do you think we nailed? Let us know in the comments! 🤣🔥
#EveryWebSeriesInSeconds #WebSeriesRecap #FastForwardComedy #IndianWebSeries #NetflixParody #AmazonPrimeSpoof

snippet.title: Battle of the Chefs: 2v2 Cooking Competition Gone Wild!
snippet.description:
🔥 Welcome to the Ultimate Cooking Showdown! 🔥

In this epic 2v2 cooking competition, we challenged two teams to create the most delicious Paneer Rolls ever! With only a limited time to cook and creativity as their main ingredient, the battle gets intense in the kitchen. 🍳

Will it be Team Blue or Team Red that impresses the judges and takes home the victory? 🏆 Watch as the teams bring their A-game, face hilarious kitchen disasters, and surprise us with their culinary skills!

👨‍🍳 The Rules:

- Both teams must prepare Paneer Rolls.
- The team with the tastiest and most creative rolls wins!

💬 Let us know in the comments which team's rolls you would love to try!

📢 Don't forget to LIKE, SUBSCRIBE, and hit the NOTIFICATION BELL to never miss an exciting challenge! 🎉

snippet.title: రే బుల్లిరాజు ఏం చేశావ్‌రా: Director Anil Ravipudi Speech | Venkatesh | Asianet News Telugu
snippet.description:
విక్టరీ వెంకటేష్‌, అనిల్‌ రావిపూడి కాంబినేషన్‌లో వచ్చిన మూడో సినిమా సంక్రాంతికి వస్తున్నాం. ఈ సంక్రాంతికి విడుదలైన సంక్రాంతికి వస్తున్నాం మూవీ సూపర్‌ సక్సెస్‌ అందుకుంది. దీంతో చిత్ర బృందం సంబరాల్లో మునిపోయింది. ఈ సందర్భంగా హైదరాబాద్‌లో నిర్వహించిన 'బ్లాక్‌బస్టర్‌ పొంగల్‌ జాతర' ఈవెంట్‌లో డైరెక్టర్‌ అనిల్‌ రావిపూడి మాట్లాడారు. సంక్రాంతికి వస్తున్నాం సినిమాని సూపర్‌ హిట్‌ చేసిన ప్రేక్షకులకు కృతజ్ఞతలు తెలిపారు.

localized.description:
విక్టరీ వెంకటేష్‌, అనిల్‌ రావిపూడి కాంబినేషన్‌లో వచ్చిన మూడో సినిమా సంక్రాంతికి వస్తున్నాం. ఈ సంక్రాంతికి విడుదలైన సంక్రాంతికి వస్తున్నాం మూవీ సూపర్‌ సక్సెస్‌ అందుకుంది. దీంతో చిత్ర బృందం సంబరాల్లో మునిపోయింది. ఈ సందర్భంగా హైదరాబాద్‌లో నిర్వహించిన 'బ్లాక్‌బస్టర్‌ పొంగల్‌ జాతర' ఈవెంట్‌లో డైరెక్టర్‌ అనిల్‌ రావిపూడి మాట్లాడారు. సంక్రాంతికి వస్తున్నాం సినిమాని సూపర్‌ హిట్‌ చేసిన ప్రేక్షకులకు కృతజ్ఞతలు తెలిపారు.

#asianetnewstelugu #sankranthikivasthunnam #victoryvenkatesh #anilravipudi #entertainment

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 31 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream - Wahaj Ali - Maya Ali - 16th January 2025 - Har Pal Geo

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Haseeb Hasan
Writer: Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar

Cast:
Wahaj Ali as Bilal Abdullah 
Maya Ali as Sadaf
Usama Khan as Ammar
Hira Mani as Hamsha
Amar Khan as Dania
Saba Hameed as Farzana
Syed Mohammed Ahmed as Namdaar
Shahvir Kadwani as Zaviyaar

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Apne Apne Shyam : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneShyamOfficial

-------------------------------------------------------------------
About Dr Kumar Vishwas :

The people who make history are the ones who not only give their life to their career but also give their career a new life. When the career is that of a poet, every step is a risk. Kumar Vishwas is one such poet who has gifted himself an era of such a popularity which other poets cant’t even dream of.
Kumar Vishwas is a poet who went beyond the stereotypical norms of ‘Kavi Sammelan’ or poetic functions and made it a performer’s stage. He has mastered and excelled in all aspects in whatever he has done. Dr Kumar Vishwas has been doing this since years just with a mic and his poems and wits in his soulful voice.
His popularity can be guessed by the fact that the audience sings his verses with him, he has crafted a new dimension by rejuvenating the structure and mechanics of Hindi poetry and Kavi Sammelan.
 
Recently, Dr. Kumar Vishwas has started hosting energy sessions popularly Known as Apne Apne Ram and Apne Apne Shyam where he talks about life skills of Shri Ram’s and Shri Krishna's life, and the applicability of the same in one’s own life to over come the challenges and social concerns we come across in our life.

snippet.description:
8th Pay Commission Updates: 8वां वेतन आयोग किस तारीख से लागू होगा, इसे लेकर अभी ऐलान नहीं किया गया है, लेकिन परंपरागत तौर पर वेतन आयोग का गठन हर 10 साल में किया जाता है. जिसमें केंद्रीय कर्मचारियों की सैलरी, भत्ते और लाभों की समीक्षा की जाती है और कोई सुझाव या बदलाव होते हैं तो उसके लिए प्रस्ताव दिए जाते हैं.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS |  Real Madrid 5-2 Celta de Vigo | Copa del Rey 2024/25
snippet.description:
Real Madrid made it through to the quarter-finals of the Copa del Rey, overcoming Celta in a hard-fought match that was settled in extra time thanks to Endrick’s brace and another from Valverde. Earlier, our team had taken a 2-0 lead after a stunning finish from Mbappé and another from Vini Jr. However, the Galicians equalised in the final minutes through Bamba and Marcos Alonso from the penalty spot. On January 20th, Ancelotti's side will learn who their opponent will be in the next round of the competition.
#LaCopaMola

es.description:
El Real Madrid logró el pase a los cuartos de final de la Copa del Rey. Venció al Celta en un partido muy disputado que se resolvió en la prórroga gracias a un doblete de Endrick y a otro gol de Valverde. Antes, nuestro equipo se había puesto por delante 2-0 tras un gran tanto de Mbappé y otro de Vini Jr. Sin embargo, los gallegos igualaron el encuentro en los minutos finales por medio de Bamba y Marcos Alonso, de penalti. El 20 de enero los de Ancelotti conocerán a su rival en la siguiente ronda de la competición.

snippet.title: 8th Pay Commission Approved for Central Government Employees | Indepth | Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
हमारी टीम द्वारा काउसलिंग लेने के लिए यह फॉर्म भरें:  https://drishti.xyz/Noida-Centre-Hindi
या फिर इस नंबर पर संपर्क करें: 8750187501
लोकेशन:  https://drishti.xyz/Drishti-IAS-Noida
*************************************************************************
Telegram link - https://web.telegram.org/k/#@indepthdrishtiias    

 The 8th Pay Commission, recently approved by the Union Cabinet ahead of the 2025 budget, is set to revise the salaries of nearly 50 lakh central government employees. This commission will not only result in salary hikes but also an adjustment in the Dearness Allowance (DA). While the exact percentage of salary hikes remains unclear, reports suggest that the fitment factor could rise from 2.57 to 2.86, which could lead to significant increases in basic pay. The new commission follows previous pay revisions under the 7th, 6th, and 5th Pay Commissions, each of which has adjusted government employee pay scales based on factors like inflation, the economy, and income disparities. Learn how pay commissions impact salaries and what employees can expect in the upcoming 8th Pay Commission. 

*************************************************************************

localized.title: 8th Pay Commission Approved for Central Government Employees | Indepth | Drishti IAS
localized.description:
हमारी टीम द्वारा काउसलिंग लेने के लिए यह फॉर्म भरें:  https://drishti.xyz/Noida-Centre-Hindi
या फिर इस नंबर पर संपर्क करें: 8750187501
लोकेशन:  https://drishti.xyz/Drishti-IAS-Noida
*************************************************************************
Telegram link - https://web.telegram.org/k/#@indepthdrishtiias    

 The 8th Pay Commission, recently approved by the Union Cabinet ahead of the 2025 budget, is set to revise the salaries of nearly 50 lakh central government employees. This commission will not only result in salary hikes but also an adjustment in the Dearness Allowance (DA). While the exact percentage of salary hikes remains unclear, reports suggest that the fitment factor could rise from 2.57 to 2.86, which could lead to significant increases in basic pay. The new commission follows previous pay revisions under the 7th, 6th, and 5th Pay Commissions, each of which has adjusted government employee pay scales based on factors like inflation, the economy, and income disparities. Learn how pay commissions impact salaries and what employees can expect in the upcoming 8th Pay Commission.
